# .cursorrules

Docker
- Use `docker compose` to control the services.
- Name of docker compose file: `compose.yaml`

File & Folder Names
- Next.js routes in kebab-case (e.g. `app/dashboard/page.tsx`).
- Shared types in `src/lib/types.ts`.

Next.js Structure
- Use App Router in `app/`. Server components by default, `"use client"` for client logic.
- Use Clerk for auth. `.env` for secrets.

Misc
- Keep code short; commits semantic.
- Use `tsx` scripts for migrations.


